  "title": "Marketing Crew (Travelling Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for motivated individuals who are eager to build real-world business skills and grow into leadership roles. This position is designed for driven people who enjoy working with others, learning fast, and taking on new challenges in a dynamic environment.</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Represent and grow client brands through face-to-face engagement and campaigns</li><li>Learn strategic communication, market positioning, and customer engagement skills</li><li>Work closely with experienced leaders through structured 1-to-1 training</li><li>Develop leadership skills by supporting, guiding, and managing a growing team</li></ul><p><u><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></u></p><ul><li>Willingness to learn, strong work ethic, and a positive attitude</li><li>Enjoys working with people and in team-based environments</li><li>Comfortable in a fast-paced, performance-driven setting</li><li>Leadership potential — no experience required, training provided</li></ul><p><u><strong>Why Join Us</strong></u></p><ul><li>Personalised 1-to-1 training</li><li>Energetic and supportive team culture</li><li>Clear career progression</li><li>⁠Travel Opportunities</li></ul>",
